## Get Rooms Request - Delegate to Lambda for user room lookup with join

{
  "version": "2018-05-29",
  "operation": "Invoke",
  "payload": {
    "action": "getUserRooms",
    "userId": "$ctx.args.userId",
    "roomType": "$util.defaultIfNull($ctx.args.roomType, '')",
    "limit": $ctx.args.limit,
    "nextToken": "$util.defaultIfNull($ctx.args.nextToken, '')",
    "identity": $util.toJson($ctx.identity)
  }
}
